    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with unilateral optic neuritis or with multiple sclerosis and an optic
             neuritis in the previous 5 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  previous history of ophthalmic and neurologic pathology

          -  anisocoria

          -  minor

          -  Patient with a measure of legal protection

          -  Pregnancy

          -  patient opposition to participation in the study

          -  no affiliation to social security
      </textblock>
